OL,6,FWorkers at North East engineering firm
OL,7,FBritish Engines are set to strike in a
OL,8,Frow over pay.
OL,10,FAround 170 employees will take
OL,11,Findustrial action after three separate
OL,12,Fballots.
OL,14,FUnite says a 3% offer from British
OL,15,FEngines is a 'real terms pay cut'
OL,16,Fgiven that current RPI figures stand
OL,17,Fat 4%.
