OL,6,F"It is disappointing that the Unite
OL,7,Fmembers of the three businesses have
OL,8,Fchosen to undertake industrial strike
OL,9,Faction from 24 - 26 May, despite
OL,10,Fmultiple offers aimed at reaching a
OL,11,Fresolution.
